==Portuguese==
===Etymology===
Literally "zero at the left": 020 equals 20; the leading zero before the 2 has no effect.

===Noun phrase===
'''[[zero]] [[à]] [[esquerda]]''', {{m}}
# A person of little worth or usefulness, a [[good-for-nothing]].
#: ''Ela se casou com João? Aquele zero à esquerda!'' &mdash; ''Did she marry John? That good-for-nothing!''